{"tid":1305417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【違反私隱】咁樣查人身份證算唔算公開展示他人姓名及身份證資料？","createTime":"2019-07-11T00:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T07:20:13.000Z","uid":37661,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"becd8aea3e06cac80112cdd791b0d28fa3d20783","tid":1305417,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:27:02.000Z","msg":"From Now 新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Cg0g1J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Cg0g1J.png&h=c19db05c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉到個報案人身份證咁高，後面又咁多人，又相機又電話影梗，應該會被人拍到報案人個身份證。<br />\n<br />\n依家係講梗佢係報案人，唔係疑犯，就算係犯都冇權公開佢身份證。<br />\n<br />\n我哋係咪要一人一信搵香港個人資料私隱專員公署問呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢個網頁有寫：<br />\n<br />\n他人將你的姓名及身分證號碼一同展示<br />\n<br />\nOrganisations should not publiclydisplay your name together with your ID card no.<br />\n<br />\n機構不應將你的姓名及身分證號碼一同公開展示。<br />\n除法律另有規定或准許外，機構應確保不會將身分證號碼及持證人的姓名一同公開展示。此外，機構亦應確保除須進行與身分證號碼的准許用途有關活動的人外，不讓其他人看見或查閱有關身分證號碼及姓名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/data_privacy_law/code_of_practices/code_guide_individual_4.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcpd.org.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fdata_privacy_law%2Fcode_of_practices%2Fcode_guide_individual_4.html&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnTHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=a159e59c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/data_privacy_law/code_of_practices/code_guide_individual_4.html</a><br />\n<br />\n提出投訴<br />\n根據條例第37條，投訴須用中文或英文以書面作出或專員所接受的其他形式而作出。投訴人可考慮填寫投訴表格(OPS001)並連同證據一併提交。為核實投訴人的身份，投訴人可親臨公署出示身份證明文件或將副本郵寄至公署。收到投訴後，公署職員會按處理投訴程序跟進個案。<br />\n<br />\n你可透過以下途徑遞交你的投訴：-<br />\n<br />\n親臨公署或郵寄<br />\n<br />\n地址:<br />\n香港灣仔皇后大道東248號陽光中心13樓1303室<br />\n<br />\n公署接待處辦公時間:<br />\n星期一至星期五︰<br />\n上午8時45分 至 下午12時45分<br />\n下午1時50分 至 下午5時40分<br />\n<br />\n傳真<br />\n你亦可以填妥投訴表格用傳真向我們查詢或投訴<br />\n傳真號碼:28777026<br />\n<br />\n電子郵遞<br />\n你可以填妥投訴表格,並轉送致以下電郵地址作出投訴<br />\ncomplaints@pcpd.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/complaints/how_complaint/complaint/complaint.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcpd.org.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcomplaints%2Fhow_complaint%2Fcomplaint%2Fcomplaint.html&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnTHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=d3103f90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/complaints/how_complaint/complaint/complaint.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff39633ded5ad4ab2518a7ff55927f44b342d27b","tid":1305417,"uid":48766,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"岩呀, 尋晚睇到都嬲<br />\n隻狗咁樣舉起張身份證擺能到明玩野"},{"pid":"7c24f97e891b415f027c2f46fce620e4d6fb2178","tid":1305417,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:30:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec638eef1ca3d3836a0e823604d6a8a2de0cc9cb","tid":1305417,"uid":37661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ff39633ded5ad4ab2518a7ff55927f44b342d27b","tid":1305417,"uid":48766,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"岩呀, 尋晚睇到都嬲<br />\n隻狗咁樣舉起張身份證擺能到明玩野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:35:02.000Z","msg":"我今朝睇完嬲撚到，出門坐車返工都係覺得唔忿氣。<br />\n<br />\n即刻裝個 Now 新聞 app<br />\n<br />\nCap 圖，最緊要係遮咗報案人<br />\n<br />\n上 Google 搵條例。<br />\n<br />\n擺上嚟！！"},{"pid":"ea9e87296e770d5682d4881583df1027413e334e","tid":1305417,"uid":258492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:52:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"596921ff55d8c3bcaa46de101c467ef629e8fa98","tid":1305417,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:54:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n死黑警"},{"pid":"834ae61a88ccbad8112907f041c8a91570d1414f","tid":1305417,"uid":272942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:59:05.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"52779cf3a6a8bb7f139c58620233bc38c461ac45","tid":1305417,"uid":124091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:04:07.000Z","msg":"推到幫狗仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ang